message.text:
From FEUCSO 88 to FEUCSO 90

I wanna tell you a story of a freshman almost three years ago. Back then, this student was hesitant to join any organization. With all the academic demands, it felt safer to just stay on the sidelines.

But one day, they decided to take a chance and applied for FEUCSO. What they found was more than just an organization, it became a safe space to grow, to belong, and to discover their own voice. It gave them the courage to step up, and the avenue to contribute to something larger than themselves.

To every freshie and Tamaraw: sometimes the best growth happens when you go beyond your comfort zone. FEUCSO, and organizations like it, can be the home where you find not only opportunities, but also the community and purpose you’ve been searching for.

And that student? That student is me. And I will never get tired of serving the student body.

Tara? Samahan nyo kami sa Legal Affairs??
https://bit.ly/FEUCSOApplicationForm

To every freshie and Tamaraw: sometimes the best growth happens when you go beyond your comfort zone. FEUCSO, and organizations like it, can be the home where you find not only opportunities, but also the community and purpose you’ve been searching for.

And that student? That student is me. And I will never get tired of serving the student body.
